  "description": "Almost entirely breath. Effort at minimum pushes the engine into whisper territory where noise dominates and only the faintest harmonic ghosts remain. The formant shape is still there — you can hear the vowel in the breath — but it is a voice remembered, not a voice present. Slow drift between A and I vowels.",
